data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!! This ABSOLUTELY GORGEOUS 4br 2bath home is a MUST SEE!!!This perfectly maintained home has so much to offer. Open concept with beautiful living room and kitchen to enjoy family. Two separate dining areas.  Kitchen island, granite counter tops, backsplash, built in cabinets, conventional and convection electric oven. Split bedroom design, with stunning master bedroom retreat and walk in closet. Ensuite master bath has dual sinks, built in cabinets, garden tub, and Tahitian tile walk in shower. Carpet and laminate flooring throughout the home, along with crown molding and decorative ceilings. Plenty of room for an office or second living area. Outside is a 10x12  storage building with electric, lighting, work bench, and plenty of shelving for storage. HVAC offers air-filtration system. Beautiful property with oak trees and private backyard to relax and enjoy the country setting. Fencing by shop conveys along with the pergola and grill. This one won't last long!
